We're all getting big, fat
raises when you become somebody.

35
00:02:25,524 --> 00:02:26,942
[Light laughter]

36
00:02:26,984 --> 00:02:29,736
Oh, did they kill
Badgley Mishka!

37
00:02:29,820 --> 00:02:31,905
Okay, laugh now, but
tomorrow it could be us.

38
00:02:31,989 --> 00:02:34,783
Not us... you.
I just make the coffee.

39
