I'm in Times Square buck naked?

85
00:05:02,598 --> 00:05:04,474
Baby doll, you're
gonna be just fine.

86
00:05:04,558 --> 00:05:07,227
Seven years ago, you were this
debutante off the plantation,

87
00:05:07,269 --> 00:05:09,521
and now you're
my steel magnolia...

88
00:05:09,605 --> 00:05:10,897
