mother you're engaged?

222
00:11:58,931 --> 00:12:00,474
Have you thought
about children?

223
00:12:01,642 --> 00:12:03,518
I'm sorry we're late.

224
00:12:03,602 --> 00:12:06,313
That shade of lipstick does
nothing for you. What kept you?

225
00:12:06,355 --> 00:12:07,856
Oh, it's none of your business.

226
00:12:07,940 --> 00:12:09,983
Ah, you know I hate surprises.
What's going on?

227
00:12:10,025 --> 00:12:12,527
Oh, Tom, always a pleasure.
Good to see you.

228
00:12:12,569 --> 00:12:14,321
...Melanie, darling.
...Hi, Your Honor.

229
00:12:14,363 --> 00:12:15,656
So good to see you.

230
00:12:15,697 --> 00:12:18,283
Look at you... always
the belle of the ball.

231
00:12:18,367 --> 00:12:20,327
I hear very good things
about your new line.

232
00:12:20,410 --> 00:12:22,079
Oh, yeah. Thanks.

233
00:12:22,162 --> 00:12:23,956
Always a pleasure.

234
00:12:26,708 --> 00:12:29,002
Um...

235
00:12:29,086 --> 00:12:30,837
...Andrew?
...Yes?

236
00:12:30,921 --> 00:12:32,172
Seems Melanie is wearing
a skating rink

237
00:12:32,214 --> 00:12:33,757
